<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 09 Oct 2024 01:06:01 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>中国在重要讲话前称台湾总统正在加剧紧张局势</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-president-is-escalating-tensions-china-says-ahead-key-speech-2024-10-09/</link><description>中国政府表示，台湾总统赖清德正在以“险恶的意图”加剧紧张局势，而赖清德将在台北发表主题演讲，这可能会引发中国的军事反应。</description><pubDate>Wed, 09 Oct 2024 00:17:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-president-is-escalating-tensions-china-says-ahead-key-speech-2024-10-09/</guid></item><item><title>优衣库所有者预计品牌海外扩张推动年利润飙升 24%</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/uniqlo-owner-seen-posting-24-annual-profit-surge-brands-overseas-push-2024-10-08/</link><description>随着品牌进军西方市场以及中国业务的复苏，休闲服装巨头优衣库的日本所有者预计将连续第三年超出自己的预期，实现创纪录的利润。</description><pubDate>Tue, 08 Oct 2024 23:22:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/uniqlo-owner-seen-posting-24-annual-profit-surge-brands-overseas-push-2024-10-08/</guid></item><item><title>日本制造商十月份信心上升，对中国的担忧挥之不去：路透社短观</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/japan/japan-manufacturers-confidence-rises-oct-concerns-over-china-linger-2024-10-08/</link><description>路透社周三的月度调查显示，日本制造商对 10 月份的商业状况变得更加有信心，但他们对中国经济复苏的步伐仍持谨慎态度。</description><pubDate>Tue, 08 Oct 2024 23:16:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/japan/japan-manufacturers-confidence-rises-oct-concerns-over-china-linger-2024-10-08/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：投资者解读美联储茶叶，摆脱中国刺激措施</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-2024-10-08/</link><description>展望未来一天的亚洲市场。</description><pubDate>Tue, 08 Oct 2024 21:47:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-2024-10-08/</guid></item><item><title>中国电动汽车制造商比亚迪预计 2025 年墨西哥电动汽车销量将增至 10 万辆</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinese-electric-carmaker-byd-sees-ev-mexico-sales-ramping-up-100000-2025-2024-10-08/</link><description>中国电动汽车制造商比亚迪墨西哥公司负责人 Jorge Vallejo 周二表示，该公司预计今年将在墨西哥销售 5 万辆电动汽车 (EV)，并于 2025 年销售 10 万辆。</description><pubDate>Tue, 08 Oct 2024 20:07:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinese-electric-carmaker-byd-sees-ev-mexico-sales-ramping-up-100000-2025-2024-10-08/</guid></item><item><title>美国商务部称雷蒙多与中国商务部长通话</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/raimondo-speaks-with-chinas-commerce-minister-us-commerce-dept-says-2024-10-08/</link><description>美国商务部表示，美国商务部长吉娜·雷蒙多周二与中国商务部部长王文涛通话，讨论了上个月举行的商业问题双边工作组会议。</description><pubDate>Tue, 08 Oct 2024 17:20:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/raimondo-speaks-with-chinas-commerce-minister-us-commerce-dept-says-2024-10-08/</guid></item><item><title>大陆集团预计第三季度欧洲和北美汽车产量下降</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/continental-expects-drop-european-north-american-car-output-third-quarter-2024-10-08/</link><description>德国汽车供应商大陆集团周二表示，预计第三季度全球乘用车和轻型卡车产量将较第二季度下降3%以上，但随着中国汽车制造商市场份额的增加，中国产量将增长约4%。</description><pubDate>Tue, 08 Oct 2024 16:03:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/continental-expects-drop-european-north-american-car-output-third-quarter-2024-10-08/</guid></item><item><title>西班牙向 Stellantis 提供 1.46 亿美元补贴，用于建设潜在的电动汽车电池工厂</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/spain-grants-146-million-subsidy-stellantis-potential-ev-battery-plant-2024-10-08/</link><description>西班牙工业部长霍尔迪·赫雷乌 (Jordi Hereu) 周二表示，西班牙已向汽车制造商 Stellantis 提供 1.33 亿欧元（1.46 亿美元）补贴，用于其位于东北部城市萨拉戈萨附近的潜在电池制造厂。</description><pubDate>Tue, 08 Oct 2024 15:38:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/spain-grants-146-million-subsidy-stellantis-potential-ev-battery-plant-2024-10-08/</guid></item><item><title>中国就土耳其电动汽车关税向世贸组织提出申诉</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/china-files-complaint-against-turkey-wto-over-electric-vehicle-tariffs-2024-10-08/</link><description>中国外交使团周二在一份声明中表示，中国已迈出第一步，就土耳其电动汽车进口关税向世界贸易组织发起贸易争端。</description><pubDate>Tue, 08 Oct 2024 15:36:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/china-files-complaint-against-turkey-wto-over-electric-vehicle-tariffs-2024-10-08/</guid></item><item><title>蒂亚福因在上海输球后愤怒地辱骂裁判而道歉</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/tennis/tiafoe-swears-umpire-furious-rant-after-loss-shanghai-2024-10-08/</link><description>周二，在上海大师赛第三轮比赛中，美国选手弗朗西斯·蒂亚福（Frances Tiafoe）在计时违例后输给罗曼·萨菲乌林（Roman Safiullin），随后他对主裁进行了脏话长篇大论。</description><pubDate>Tue, 08 Oct 2024 15:33:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/tennis/tiafoe-swears-umpire-furious-rant-after-loss-shanghai-2024-10-08/</guid></item><item><title>独家：布鲁塞尔在电动汽车纠纷中拒绝了中国关于最低销售价格3万欧元的提议</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/brussels-rejected-china-proposal-30000-euro-minimum-sales-price-ev-dispute-2024-10-08/</link><description>三名消息人士称，布鲁塞尔拒绝了中国政府关于中国制造的进口电动汽车售价最低为 30,000 欧元（32,946 美元）的提议，北京方面希望此举能避免欧盟下个月征收关税。</description><pubDate>Tue, 08 Oct 2024 15:22:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/brussels-rejected-china-proposal-30000-euro-minimum-sales-price-ev-dispute-2024-10-08/</guid></item><item><title>中国对美国芯片和车联网政策表示担忧</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/china-expresses-concern-over-us-chip-connected-vehicle-policies-2024-10-08/</link><description>中国商务部长周二就美国对华半导体政策和对中国车联网的限制向美国商务部长提出“严重关切”，呼吁取消对中国企业的制裁。</description><pubDate>Tue, 08 Oct 2024 14:25:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/china-expresses-concern-over-us-chip-connected-vehicle-policies-2024-10-08/</guid></item><item><title>TikTok被13个州和华盛顿特区起诉，被指控伤害年轻用户</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/legal/tiktok-sued-by-13-states-dc-accused-harming-younger-users-2024-10-08/</link><description>TikTok 周二面临美国 13 个州和哥伦比亚特区提起的新诉讼，指控这个流行的社交媒体平台伤害并未能保护年轻人。</description><pubDate>Tue, 08 Oct 2024 14:03:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/legal/tiktok-sued-by-13-states-dc-accused-harming-younger-users-2024-10-08/</guid></item><item><title>由于投资者等待通胀数据，华尔街因科技股买盘收高</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/futures-tick-higher-with-inflation-data-earnings-view-2024-10-08/</link><description>华尔街基准指数周二收盘，收复前一交易日的部分跌幅，因投资者重新买入科技股，投资者将注意力转向即将公布的通胀数据和第三季度财报季的开始。</description><pubDate>Tue, 08 Oct 2024 10:18:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/futures-tick-higher-with-inflation-data-earnings-view-2024-10-08/</guid></item><item><title>电动汽车关税举措后，中国在欧盟贸易中针锋相对地瞄准白兰地</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/china-puts-anti-dumping-measures-brandy-imports-eu-2024-10-08/</link><description>这些措施打击了轩尼诗和人头马等法国品牌。</description><pubDate>Tue, 08 Oct 2024 05:54:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/china-puts-anti-dumping-measures-brandy-imports-eu-2024-10-08/</guid></item></channel></rss>